description:
Eat vegan food in Mexico City! Welcome to Rated V for Vegan where I excite you about vegan food and travel. Join me today as I show you where to eat vegan food in Mexico City and where to enjoy iconic foods like al pastor tacos, tortas and churros. 

Get the Ultimate Vegan Guide to Spain https://www.ratedvfood.com/ebook
Let's connect on Instagram http://www.instagram.com/ratedvfood

Use the Happy Cow App to find more Amazing vegan options in Mexico City! They even have a map function and lots of details about what options each restaurant has. Download Here https://www.happycow.net/mobile

RESTAURANTS:
Por Siempre Vegana Al Pastor Tacos & Molcajete 0:26 - 5:12
https://www.instagram.com/por_siempre_vegana_taqueria/

Vegamo Pan de Muerto 5:21
https://www.instagram.com/vegamo.romanorte/

Xochimilco Boat Canal 5:40

Churros El Moro 6:50
https://www.instagram.com/churreriaelmoro/

Gatorta Vegan Tortats 9:05
https://www.instagram.com/gatorta_/

La Michoacana Paleta de Coco (agua) 10:22

La Pitahaya Vegana 
https://www.instagram.com/lapitahayavegana/

Do you want to know which cities are the most vegan-friendly? Or perhaps you'd like to learn how to prepare simple vegan dishes and gain a better understanding of the vegan lifestyle? Well, then you're in luck! Subscribe to ensure that you don't miss a post.  Please consider subscribing to our channel: ►►SUBSCRIBE: https://cutt.ly/RatedVforVegan

Join me as I show you where you can find some of the best vegan food in the world, as well as city guides, new recipes, and vegan product reviews. And if you want to know more about my vegan lifestyle as a vegan food blogger, then you should check out all my videos. Travel, recipes, and food reviews will accompany me on my plant-based adventure.

Watch more vegan lifestyle videos
VEGAN NYC https://youtu.be/JayXCkfNhSc
VEGAN MADRID https://youtu.be/7nCp-YYCOI4
VEGAN CHICAGO https://youtu.be/7zbDdNRLg4E
 
My channel comprises several videos ranging from my vegan lifestyle, how I put together my vegan recipes, how I intake my vegan protein, and then most important of them all, how I achieve intuitive living. 

You can join me on this journey by clicking the subscribe link below. Subscribe now to get my latest vlogs! ►►SUBSCRIBE: https://cutt.ly/RatedVforVegan
 
Thank you for being here!
Stay Safe and Healthy,
 
Rated V for Vegan
